data.description:
Welcome to this move-in-ready home featuring a private backyard pool oasis. With spacious rooms, soaring ceilings, and abundant natural light, this home offers a serene ambiance. The kitchen, with a cooktop island and peninsula, connects seamlessly to the grand living area. Enjoy pool views from the backyard, and upstairs, find three large bedrooms and a game room. The main floor includes a study, dining area, breakfast nook, and laundry. Appliances are included, and recent updates, including solar panels which offset a large portion of you monthly eclectic bill and a new roof, enhance the home's appeal. Professional Pool Maintenance included. SOME PHOTOS ARE VIRTURALLY STATGED. Don't miss out on this meticulously cared-for home! Schedule an appointment to see it in person today!

Smoking allowed:No
